{"tid":1885930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伍公子：市民要學習監察政府部門及議員","createTime":"2020-02-18T15:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T14:24:24.000Z","uid":60916,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"30f845b4e2316bcd6251940f36d478bd5acd20d8","tid":1885930,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:21:14.000Z","msg":"今年，我將會致力提升香港政治質素。<br />\n<br />\n我只有兩個目標：<br />\n<br />\n一，議員要連接網絡，與市民溝通。<br />\n<br />\n二，市民要學習監察政府部門及議員。<br />\n<br />\n於社會上流，當疫症將所有人都逼在室內，社會賢達才驚覺互聯網的價值。<br />\n<br />\n於社會下流，人民只關心藝人黃藍，卻不顧議會投票結果。<br />\n<br />\n時乘立法會選舉，2020將象徵香港政治新的一頁。<br />\n<br />\n我會將香港議員放進YouTube，讓香港人當成娛樂一般好好觀察，一舉扭轉香港汙腐風氣。<br />\n<br />\n為進入立法會，政治老人也要學習做YouTuber。<br />\n<br />\n你們要為點擊開心，為訂閲憂心，為留言傷心。<br />\n<br />\n而我將為大家親手套上噹啷作響的YouTuber大頸圈。<br />\n<br />\nCredit: Loui5Ng 伍公子<br />\n<br />\n連伍公子都叫你地好好監察議員啊<br />\n你班泛民打手維穩機器唔好一味盲撐啦<br />\n監察議員啊矇炳"},{"pid":"922ae5dabec0a66202bd9a64972c5cf08e50f32e","tid":1885930,"uid":47080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"伍公子真係好前"},{"pid":"73740b01b4fd1d8b67ed9e6fdfaeab452a1e4f4f","tid":1885930,"uid":147895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:30:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31ae7787d72516ae2367140b74fec57439767f44","tid":1885930,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e680fb167aa2ebb1f896bf1125e2d4363aeb15","tid":1885930,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9181daab7e0764c574d7d5150fd59f87771b5157","tid":1885930,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a06c98da4ff7e9f62a04af36e8c97119769b9e1b","tid":1885930,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply